{"content": "500 Ladies is an epic project dreamed up by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/firstladyNFT\">FirstLady </a>to hand make 500 Ladies. Each was handcrafted into an actual miniature lady complete with flowing dresses and manufactured heads.\n<figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">I remember as a child selling a hand knitted doll I made for $1. That was a magic moment. But NFT’s is a different story 😊</p>\n— First Lady NFT (@firstladynft) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/firstladynft/status/1455320213021347843?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 1, 2021</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure>\n<em>\"All the ladies are distinct individuals, and can be thought of as representing the huge variety of roles for women in contemporary society, from mothers to doctors and from engineers to artists.\" says FirstLady.</em>\n<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img class=\"kg-image\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.27.35-PM-1200x673.png\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1_Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.27.35-PM.png 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2_Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.27.35-PM.png 1000w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3_Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.27.35-PM-1200x674.png 1600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4_Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.27.35-PM-1200x674.png 2400w\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1122\" /></figure>\n<em>\"500 Ladies also blurs and merges stereotypical ideas of male and female work. The combination of crafted and manufactured objects highlights the similarities between men and women, rather than their differences, in that they have both had a role in creating objects and a role as a means of creation.\" says FirstLady.</em>\n\nThe collection of 500 is being released 100 at a time. You can collect points with each lady that can be redeemed for epic FREE airdrops. For example, search for ladies with higher points. If your collection of ladies is 2,500+ or higher, you will receive a personalised NFT displaying your individual colllection of ladies together.\n<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img class=\"kg-image\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.28.42-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"510\" height=\"302\" />\n<figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/500ladies?search[numericTraits][0][name]=Points&amp;search[numericTraits][0][ranges][0][min]=399&amp;search[numericTraits][0][ranges][0][max]=497&amp;search[sortAscending]=false&amp;search[sortBy]=LAST_SALE_DATE\">Collect multiple ladies with higher points</a> to be eligible for a personalised collection airdrop.</figcaption></figure>\n<a href=\"https://www.500ladies.xyz/roadmap/\">Roadmaps</a> give collectors certainty and sometimes a cause. This art project does both. It rewards women artists in NFT's by reinvesting a considerable proportion of sales back into female artists...because yes we all know that the space needs balancing up.\n<figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">Sometimes I draw a quick sketch of a lady in this handmade book. <a href=\"https://t.co/iXmUesszaX\">pic.twitter.com/iXmUesszaX</a></p>\n— First Lady NFT (@firstladynft) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/firstladynft/status/1455375046629904387?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 2, 2021</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure>\nYou can stroll through an OnCyber gallery to get the full impact of seeing 100 of the 500 Ladies together in one place.\n<figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">There is a roadmap to reward collectors of multiple ladies.<a href=\"https://t.co/PJbmMeFlPX\">https://t.co/PJbmMeFlPX</a></p>\n...or pick up one that you like...one that speaks to you like they all speak to me.\n\n12/12\n\n— First Lady NFT (@firstladynft) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/firstladynft/status/1455042750085091331?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 1, 2021</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure>\n<em>\"I was always taught that you have to get everything down on paper before you start creating, but my brain doesn't work like that. I just started creating and then more ideas came.\" says First Lady.</em>\n<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img class=\"kg-image\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/NFT-Ladies-092-800x800.jpg\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1_NFT-Ladies-092.jpg 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2_NFT-Ladies-092-800x800.jpg 1000w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3_NFT-Ladies-092-800x800.jpg 1600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4_NFT-Ladies-092-800x800.jpg 2400w\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" />\n<figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/22603120525120236904336132415769835749351751882947872171728546649002699915265\">Lady #092 on OpenSea</a> at 0.04 eth</figcaption></figure>\nThere are <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/500ladies?search[sortAscending]=true&amp;search[sortBy]=PRICE&amp;search[stringTraits][0][name]=Rares&amp;search[stringTraits][0][values][0]=AC%20%2F%20DC&amp;search[stringTraits][0][values][1]=Afro&amp;search[stringTraits][0][values][2]=Electric%20Girl&amp;search[stringTraits][0][values][3]=The%20Artist&amp;search[stringTraits][0][values][4]=The%20Connector\">Rares</a> with names like AC/DC, Afro, Electric Girl, The Artist and The Collector.\n<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img class=\"kg-image\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/NFT-Ladies-094-800x800.jpg\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1_NFT-Ladies-094.jpg 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2_NFT-Ladies-094-800x800.jpg 1000w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3_NFT-Ladies-094-800x800.jpg 1600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4_NFT-Ladies-094-800x800.jpg 2400w\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" />\n<figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/22603120525120236904336132415769835749351751882947872171728546651201723170817\">The Connector Lady</a> #094 on OpenSea</figcaption></figure>\nYou can also sort by the accessory each Lady carries such as Handbag, bracelet, belt, necklace, scarf... or the rarers of feather boa, trousers and diamond buttons!\n<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img class=\"kg-image\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.39.51-PM-1200x534.png\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1_Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.39.51-PM.png 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2_Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.39.51-PM.png 1000w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3_Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.39.51-PM-1200x534.png 1600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4_Screen-Shot-2021-11-02-at-4.39.51-PM-1200x534.png 2400w\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"890\" />\n<figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/500ladies?search[sortAscending]=true&amp;search[sortBy]=PRICE&amp;search[stringTraits][0][name]=Accessory&amp;search[stringTraits][0][values][0]=Handbag&amp;search[stringTraits][0][values][1]=Bracelet\">Sort by a\nccessory style showing handbags and bracelets</a></figcaption></figure>\n<em>\"The contemporary women of 500 Ladies can be whoever they want to be and, collectively, make a positive statement about what the future will look like.\" says FirstLady.</em>\n\n<a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/500ladies?search[sortAscending]=false&amp;search[sortBy]=LISTING_DATE\">View the 500 Ladies collection on OpenSea</a>.\n\n<hr />\n\n<strong><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\">Subscribe to MintFace</a> and receive new artist features by email.</strong>\n\nIf this article has made you curious about getting started with digital art, we also run the <a href=\"https://maven.com/cache/nft-digital-artist-economy\">Digital Artist Economy workshop</a> helping artists create their first digital art through a <a href=\"https://maven.com/cache/nft-digital-artist-economy\">three week programme.</a> Share it with an artist you'd like to see on an NFT marketplace.\n\n<strong>MintFace surfaces great artists and artworks so you don't have to. </strong>\n\n<em>Enjoying MintFace? Subscribe for $9 per month.</em>"}